{"tid":1238903,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"稱林鄭今將撤回修訂再道歉 《大公》網頁社評突被刪走","createTime":"2019-06-18T03:46:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T08:12:26.000Z","uid":28114,"like":22,"dislike":230,"uniUserReply":78,"replies":[{"pid":"7bfe8bedffd6f96c4423d1a688ce3f522a51b940","tid":1238903,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T03:46:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190618/large/1560822593_ac00.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190618%2Flarge%2F1560822593_ac00.jpg&h=3488e1ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(資料圖片)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190618/large/1560826200_d037.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190618%2Flarge%2F1560826200_d037.png&h=05859d73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《大公報》網頁社評連結突失效，未能閱讀有關文章。<br />\n<br />\n特首林鄭月娥上周六宣佈暫緩《逃犯條例》修訂，但未能平息市民怒火，繼續要求政府將條例完全撤回、撤銷6.12對示威者的控罪，以及林鄭下台等，在周日200萬人上街後，林鄭以書面向市民道歉，但並無現身。林鄭今日將會見傳媒，據《大公報》今日社評指，估計林鄭今日將會宣布正式撤回條例草案及再度作出「誠摯」道歉，形容「這是一種非常謙卑和認真的處事態度，顯示的是為政者應有的道德勇氣和責任承擔，值得給予理解和支持」。但其後在《大公報》網頁，此篇社評的連結已失效，文章被刪去，只餘下﻿標題「支持林鄭依法施政 發展經濟改善民生」，但未能觀看內容。<br />\n<br />\n另外，原定6月12日舉行的行政長官質詢時間早前因立法會後有大批反對《逃犯條例》修訂二讀的市民聚集，立法會秘書處將質詢改期至稍後日期舉行，今日立法會網頁資料則顯示，下一次的行政長官質詢時間，將於7月3日舉行，意味行政長官質詢時間延至7月1日後。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190618/59728784?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190618%2F59728784%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=7EcP4%2BvGpl6inSsjOqiUXj2nqaxvu5zgGSEBmbQkQbg%3D&h=9e91defa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190618%2F59728784%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=fe9e1a63\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190618/59728784?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"5aa012f5598250f7512651a3eaa392e68fcb588f","tid":1238903,"uid":28114,"like":293,"dislike":0,"score":293,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T03:46:55.000Z","msg":"道你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"933a4cc31b505ab714c773025165eda017d72a1e","tid":1238903,"uid":73619,"like":193,"dislike":0,"score":193,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T03:47:54.000Z","msg":"Everyday there is a new lie<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64ad2eea60c9040aa65333447a7cb983b6b34d3a","tid":1238903,"uid":49004,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T03:48:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4404eca09ac130db611ed157239fd88b0272dede","tid":1238903,"uid":53003,"like":65,"dislike":0,"score":65,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T03:50:05.000Z","msg":"捉完棋未啊你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e94a9d74b6b5a3a58a84b275d63ff32a339d8023","tid":1238903,"uid":156611,"like":229,"dislike":0,"score":229,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T03:50:31.000Z","msg":"柒婆諗諗下都係唔忿氣？<br />\n我好撚打得架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dbc85ed7017b958a737532fd2de325aa4139cc3","tid":1238903,"uid":25183,"like":107,"dislike":0,"score":107,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T03:50:40.000Z","msg":"大公報都放流料？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6390e3e758747c5a8fbb11a549d